# Project: podos-next

## Tech Stack

- **Next.js 16** — App Router, `app/` at project root
- **React 19** — Server Components by default
- **Payload CMS 3.x** — admin at `/admin`, API at `/api`
- **PostgreSQL** via `@payloadcms/db-postgres`
- **SCSS Modules** — component-scoped styles (no Tailwind utility classes)
- **TypeScript** — strict mode
- **i18n**: `pl` (default), `ua` — via `[locale]` dynamic segment
- **Domain**: `https://podoswroclaw.pl`

## Language

- All code, comments, variable names, commit messages — **English**
- User-facing text lives in `src/translations/{pl,ua}/*.json`
